{"tid":1065064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那小學外有成年蝗當街亂砍　17幼蝗受傷","createTime":"2019-03-17T04:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T04:31:51.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef20beda54cf983d29b219204298554671d6227b","tid":1065064,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"中國河北唐山光華道小學附近，今日下午傳出有男子當街亂砍小學生，17名受傷學生被全部送院救治，沒有生命危險。<br />\n <br />\n警方通報指，今日下午1時26分許，唐山光華道小學附近發生砍人案，54歲嫌犯崔振江已被警方控制，區委、區政府迅速啟動應急預案，領導第一時間趕到現場。目前案件正由警方偵辦中，尚未知崔男行兇的原因。<br />\n <br />\n現場影片所見，光華道小學正門外，該處已被圍起封鎖，附近不少市民圍觀；至少有一名學生躺在病床上，疑似是嫌犯的中年男子則被當場制服，其雙手及地上染有大量血跡。"},{"pid":"8c40512fc11a1e1507552e71062fd8cf3234d7fe","tid":1065064,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"良心發現既成年蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔比下一代再危害地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bcd3596407f37f025bc2f125dacad8fe1b3c59","tid":1065064,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:07:18.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n根本不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4669dfd68bef0a0fb4189ad346c502a82cbe20","tid":1065064,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"抵"},{"pid":"7a0736f09882b0b5189a7a1a9c2fd236a706b336","tid":1065064,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">17名受傷學生被全部送院救治，沒有生命危險</span></blockquote><br />\n刀手渣ga，一個都殺唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫院：有17個傷者，發達了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d1c0b8b13a51998660d826536ef5e9674a9bc6","tid":1065064,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"片呢？"},{"pid":"f2a44a528953cbb94a86c7479663188dc5c65f25","tid":1065064,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"支那甩咗個頭都叫輕傷，炸開斬到十八碌叫重傷，有背景重要報保險先叫死亡"},{"pid":"f920bcf2cdd47d69fdf48a67924e55f86896c830","tid":1065064,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起中國反駁美國人權報告，<br />\n話美國有槍擊案，所以美國冇人權<br />\n<br />\nBTW，中國從來都冇發現過，<br />\n一定係有外國勢力界入或者惡意作新聞"},{"pid":"3bc2d93c1a490ad1f9f6df76d5296da262bd21a2","tid":1065064,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"把刀假架"}]}